	<h3>A brief introduction to ReviewIt</h3>
	<p>
		Review is a site created with the premise that everyone has an opinion on everything and in this day and age, people like to share those opinions with whoever will hear them.
		We created ReviewIt so that anyone can share their opinions on ANYTHING and get other peoples opinions too.
	</p>	
